{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"c779808dcc","title":"同济大学陈怀璋等右派分子的言论","origin":"同济大学马列主义资料室编印《右派分子言论汇编》第二辑（内部资料不得外传），一九五七年十月。","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"15994626fe","index":0,"year":1957,"month":5,"day":null,"articleId":"c779808dcc"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"CCRD-fanyou","name":"中国反右运动数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[{"id":"98f03a4072","name":"同济大学"}]},"publication_details":{"CCRD-fanyou":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"e94c274651","type":"title","text":"同济大学陈怀璋等右派分子的言论","index":0,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"c779808dcc"},{"id":"02260583d3","type":"authors","text":"同济大学","index":1,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"c779808dcc"},{"id":"0fcaada4f6","type":"paragraph","text":"速中语文教师  陈怀璋","index":2,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"c779808dcc"},{"id":"ae8c95b993","type":"paragraph","text":"污蔑说：“交大迁校问题，第一次周总理的指示精神传达后，大家都不愿意讨论。”","index":3,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"c779808dcc"},{"id":"a1495fdcac","type":"paragraph","text":"他指示他在交大读书的女儿（团支书）说：“如果坚持周总理的意见，陷于孤立时，该走群众路线，反对交大的迁校。”（见校刊121期第六版）","index":4,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"c779808dcc"},{"id":"34d1e07cb3","type":"paragraph","text":"速中语文教师  余力容","index":5,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"c779808dcc"},{"id":"9fba93cd9f","type":"paragraph","text":"他深受胡风的文风，路翎的才华。他说：“过去周作人（汉奸）的成就要比鲁迅高。”（见校刊120期第六版）","index":6,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"c779808dcc"},{"id":"4e6ccb9bc2","type":"paragraph","text":"建筑系毕业生  鲍锦清","index":7,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"c779808dcc"},{"id":"082738a485","type":"paragraph","text":"‘乱世出佳人’，我希望战争，因为只有世界大乱的时候，才可能出现漂亮的女人。”（摘自建筑系毕业生鲍锦清材料）","index":8,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"c779808dcc"},{"id":"becc007c8f","type":"paragraph","text":"卫生工程系毕业生  徐家基","index":9,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"c779808dcc"},{"id":"b17105d14f","type":"paragraph","text":"污蔑工商业社会主义改造说：“政府没有办法才这样做的，否则老板无法维持下去。”“私人财产被国家拿去了。”“地主收租不是剥削。”（摘正卫生工程系毕业生徐家基材料）","index":10,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"c779808dcc"},{"id":"154ece920b","type":"paragraph","text":"结构系毕业生  宋开爽","index":11,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"c779808dcc"},{"id":"e9129f5de2","type":"paragraph","text":"“在社会主义社会里，人是没有理想的，有理想就要带来痛苦。”（摘自结构系毕业生宋开爽材料）","index":12,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"c779808dcc"},{"id":"3d00a70472","type":"paragraph","text":"道桥系毕业生  韩炳权","index":13,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"c779808dcc"},{"id":"733f1acc8f","type":"paragraph","text":"支持李康年定息廿年谬论说：“这种定息没有什么和工人商量的必要。工人也是自私自利的。”（摘自道桥系毕业生韩炳权材料）","index":14,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"c779808dcc"},{"id":"ff4cc656b7","type":"paragraph","text":"建筑系毕业生  葛奇龙","index":15,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"c779808dcc"},{"id":"273c10ec35","type":"paragraph","text":"“定息五年不能赎回资本家所有财产。”完全和章乃器一唱一和。（摘自建筑系毕业生葛奇龙材料）","index":16,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"c779808dcc"},{"id":"23996fb1ae","type":"paragraph","text":"道桥系毕业生  熊寿彭","index":17,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"c779808dcc"},{"id":"3864ffa0a8","type":"paragraph","text":"在宿舍谈论李康年提出定息二十年的问题时，有人提出让工人讨论讨论，听听工人意见。熊轻蔑地说：“要给工人讨论，半年也不要。”（摘自道桥系毕业生熊寿彭材料）","index":18,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"c779808dcc"},{"id":"4088b0ccfe","type":"paragraph","text":"卫生工程系毕业生  汪涵祥","index":19,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"c779808dcc"},{"id":"a4a40ce362","type":"paragraph","text":"“进同济四年来自己一点进步也没有，就是有的话，也是书本与电影对我帮助，所得到的是人情世故懂得不少了。”（摘自卫生工程系毕业生汪涵祥材料）","index":20,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"c779808dcc"},{"id":"f1a37a16d6","type":"appellation","text":"铁路系毕业生  程印冰","index":21,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"c779808dcc"},{"id":"965eceb8db","type":"paragraph","text":"“统一分配不是祖国和个人之间的矛盾，而是同学与同学之间的矛盾。”（摘自铁路系毕业生程印冰材料）","index":22,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"c779808dcc"}],"page":{"id":"73189d2e49","publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"c779808dcc","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}